</p>

<p>
As part of my role I: 
</p>
<ul class="unordered-list">
 <li class="unordered-list__list-item">Grew the design team from 5 to almost 60 in 3 years</li>
 <li class="unordered-list__list-item">Worked with stakeholders at all levels to raise awareness and visibility of what good design looks like</li>
 <li class="unordered-list__list-item">Supported designers across multiple projects and business areas, building a community of practice and supporting their learning and development goals</li>
 <li class="unordered-list__list-item">Established the discipline of Service Design in Defra, created the right spaces for servie designers to work in and hired the first permanent team members</li>
 <li class="unordered-list__list-item">Influenced the procurement process for consultancies, partners, websites, and services. Helping to make sure the things we buy meet our own and Government’s design standards</li>
