<ul class="unordered-list">
  <li class="unordered-list__list-item"><b>A component</b> - which is a single thing that could be used on multiple products and services </li>
  <li class="unordered-list__list-item"><b>A Product</b>  - which is a single interaction by a user with the organisation, usually one step in a larger user journey 
</li>
  <li class="unordered-list__list-item"><b>A Service</b> - A service has multiple touch-points or interactions and that’s where a service designer should be.
</li>
</ul>

